				\begin{document}$$160\,{\hbox {g}\,\hbox {L}^{-1}}$$\end{document}, and dissolved organic carbon (DOC) concentrations from 0.1 to 30.1gL-1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
