				\begin{document}$$5\,\hbox {g}\,\hbox {L}^{-1}$$\end{document} due to locally restricted areas where mixing with Tertiary aquifers can occur (Wolfgramm and Seibt 2008). The fluids of the MB are described as Ca–(Na)–(Mg)-HCO3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
