They identified 48 organic compounds from 6 homologous series, belonging to (in order of predominance) n-alkanes, aromatics, S-bearing and O-bearing hydrocarbons. Further investigation of the aromatic hydrocarbons revealed also the occurrence of compounds with two or more aromatic rings. The carbon chain length of the 24 identified n-alkanes ranged from C10\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
